definition: horse/CL:匹[pi3]/horse or cavalry piece in Chinese chess/knight in Western chess
surname Ma/abbr. for Malaysia 馬來西亞|马来西亚[Ma3 lai2 xi1 ya4]
to pull/to play (a bowed instrument)/to drag/to draw/to chat

sentences.english: Malabo is one of the schools that is affected annually.
sentences.chinese: 馬拉博就是其中一所每年都被影響的學校。

sentences.english: Around the same time, bush-meat sales increased in Malabo.
sentences.chinese: 與此同時馬拉博的叢林肉銷售量猛增。

sentences.english: And we are working to bring this right to Malabo.
sentences.chinese: 而我們正在努力將這個權利帶到馬拉博。
